color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 315.85pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-left-color: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"text-indent: 14.7pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 9pt\\\\\">采矿权人因企业合并、分立</span><span style=\\\\\"letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 9pt\\\\\">,</span><span style=\\\\\"letter-spacing: 0.4pt; font-size: 9pt\\\\\">与他人合资、合作经营，因企业资产出售以及其他变更资产产权的情形而需要变更采矿权主体时，经依法批准可以将采矿权转让他人采矿。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"151\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 113.05pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 15pt\\\\\">政策法规依据</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"421\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 315.85pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-left-color: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">《矿产资源开采登记办法》（国务院241号令）</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"151\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 113.05pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 15pt\\\\\">事项申办条件</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"421\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 315.85pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-left-color: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"line-height: 200%; font-size: 12pt\\\\\">资料齐全，符合条件者到国土资源窗口上报。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"151\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 113.05pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 15pt\\\\\">申</span></div>\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 15pt\\\\\">报</span></div>\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 15pt\\\\\">材</span></div>\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 15pt\\\\\">料</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td width=\\\\\"421\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 315.85pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-left-color: #ece9d8; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div style=\\\\\"line-height: 13pt; text-indent: 18pt\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">申请报告（说明转让原因，税费缴纳情况和矿山现状）；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">采矿权转让申请书；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">转让人和受让人签订的采矿权转让合同<b>；</b>矿区范围图以及地理位置示意图；由有关国土资源管理部门出具的采矿权属无争议的证明材料；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">缴纳采矿权使用费、采矿权价款、矿产资源补偿费和资源税的证明材料复印件；出具采矿权价款缴纳评估结果确认书、采矿权价款鉴定的合同。采矿权价款属分期缴纳且未缴清的，应在转让合同中明确剩余采矿权价款的处置方案，受让人提交缴款承诺书（原件）；原占用矿产资源储量登记书复印件；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">矿山占用资源储量核查报告或结算报告及审查意见、备案文件。<b>转让申请人还需提交：</b></span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">企业法人营业执照</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">复印件；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">采矿许可证正</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">、</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">副本</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">复印件；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">矿产资源开采情况的报告</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">属于</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">国有矿山企业的，应出具主管部门的</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">批准文件</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">（或在《采矿权转让申请书》上签署的意见，原件）；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">再次转让的，应附具原转让审批文件。<b>受让人还需提交：</b>矿山企业名称核准通知书或工商营业执照及股份组成说明；能满足采矿投入的资信证明；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">受让人资质证明文件（含技术人员、设备清单等）；</span><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 9pt\\\\\">受让人按照原备案的矿产资源开发利用方案进行生产的承诺书；国土资源部门要求的其它资料。</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n        </tr>\r\n        <tr>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"151\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; border-left: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 113.05pt; padding-right: 5.4pt; border-right: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-top: 0cm\\\\\">\r\n            <div align=\\\\\"center\\\\\"><span style=\\\\\"font-size: 15pt\\\\\">办理处理流程</span></div>\r\n            </td>\r\n            <td valign=\\\\\"top\\\\\" width=\\\\\"421\\\\\" style=\\\\\"border-bottom: windowtext 1pt solid; padding-bottom: 0cm; background-color: transparent; border-top-color: #ece9d8; padding-left: 5.4pt; width: 315.85pt; pad